Data Sources
------------

This software fetches data from the following public sources at runtime.
Each source is subject to its own terms of use. No source data is bundled
with or redistributed by this software.

  UN News           https://news.un.org
  ReliefWeb         https://reliefweb.int
  Al Jazeera        https://www.aljazeera.com
  BBC News          https://www.bbc.co.uk/news
  The Guardian      https://www.theguardian.com
  New York Times    https://www.nytimes.com
  France 24         https://www.france24.com
  Times of Israel   https://www.timesofisrael.com

